title: HARRY O -- For the Love of Money ( Harry moves to Santa Monica )
description:
Because it was getting too expensive to film in San Diego, the producers decided to have Orwell move to Santa Monica with this mid-season episode. Harry explained in a voiceover that the case he was working on was the reason.  Anthony Zerbe was brought in as LAPD Lt. Trench.

Guest Stars -- Sharon Farrell, Bernie Kopell, Joe Silver, 
Mariclare Costello, Fred Bier, and Sabrina Scharf
